  <entry>
    <title>SCP:SL服务器架设教程[Linux/Windows]</title>
    <link href="http://wooxin.xyz/posts/2d18f38f.html"/>
    <id>http://wooxin.xyz/posts/2d18f38f.html</id>
    <published>2023-01-09T04:32:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-01-12T06:31:23.334Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h2 id="一：准备工作-amp-前言"><a href="#一：准备工作-amp-前言" class="headerlink" title="一：准备工作 &amp; 前言"></a>一：准备工作 &amp; 前言</h2><blockquote><ol><li>一台电脑（Linux&#x2F;Windows）</li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="2"><li>SCP：SL与MineCraft不大相同，SCP：SL不太吃CPU主频，但和MineCraft一样也是吃单核性能的<br>所以我们不必过于苛求CPU主频，只需要保证主频稳定在3.0GHz以上即可保证40人畅玩</li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="3"><li>事先声明！SCP：SL这个B游戏如果想要上服务器列表你必须有一个固定的IP，否则是没办法上列表的，方法如下：<br>3.1 <strong>内网穿透</strong>：此方法可以获得一个固定的虚拟公网IP，一定程度上来说是可以申请上服务器列表的，但是稳定性与安全性不够！<br>3.2 <strong>服务器托管</strong>：把你的机箱扔去托管，可以获得一个固定IP，缺点就是贵！<br>3.3 <strong>云服务器</strong>：这是下下策，又贵又垃圾，并不推荐<br>3.4 <strong>接一条专线</strong>：这…如果你腰缠万贯确实可以选择，但某些地方的运营商不会允许家庭接专线</li></ol></blockquote><hr><h2 id="二：服务器部署-Windows"><a href="#二：服务器部署-Windows" class="headerlink" title="二：服务器部署[Windows]"></a>二：服务器部署[Windows]</h2><blockquote><ol><li>Windows系统开服相对方便，只需要下载一个Steam并搜索下载SCP：SL<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/11/pSnyRQe.png"></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="2"><li>下载安装成功后，从你的游戏列表找到<strong>SCP Secret Laboratory Dedicated Server</strong><br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/11/pSnyfLd.png"><br>双击打开该应用，接着会弹出CMD窗口并有如下选项<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/11/pSnyIot.png"></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="3"><li>选项<br>端口号：Port number (default: 7777)<br>一般来说选择默认即可（按回车）</li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="4"><li>当看到 <strong>Waiting for players…</strong> 时就代表服务器已经开启成功了！<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/11/pSn69YV.png"></li></ol></blockquote><hr><h2 id="三：服务器部署-Linux"><a href="#三：服务器部署-Linux" class="headerlink" title="三：服务器部署[Linux]"></a>三：服务器部署[Linux]</h2><blockquote><p>Linux教程使用的工具是<a href="https://www.xshell.com/zh/free-for-home-school/"><strong>Xftp</strong></a>和<a href="https://www.xshell.com/zh/free-for-home-school/"><strong>Xshell</strong></a>）</p></blockquote><blockquote><ol><li>Linux部署SCP：SL服务器的方法和上面Windows差不多，不过要安装的不是Steam，而是SteamCMD<br>安装SteamCmd之前，我们要先安装i686和libicu，这是一个必不可少的步骤 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Centos：yum -y install glibc.i686 libstdc++.i686</span><br><span class="line">Centos：yum -y install libicu</span><br><span class="line">Ubuntu：sudo apt-get install lib32gcc</span><br><span class="line">Ubuntu：sudo apt-get install libicu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="2"><li>安装好i686后就可以进行SteamCmd的安装了<br>我们先来创建一个文件夹，用来存放SteamCmd的文件 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> SteamCmd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>然后安装wget用于下载SteamCmd <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Centos：yum -y install wget</span><br><span class="line">Ubuntu：sudo apt-get wget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>进入刚刚创建的SteamCmd文件夹 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> SteamCmd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>直接用wget下载SteamCmd <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.<span class="built_in">net</span>/client/installer/steamcmd_linux.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/11/pSnRHKO.png"><br>解压SteamCmd，然后可以从Xftp看到SteamCmd文件夹出现了一个可以运行的steamcmd.sh文件 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxf steamcmd_linux.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/11/pSnWEIs.png"></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="3"><li>运行SteamCmd，等待SteamCmd更新完成 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./steamcmd.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/11/pSnfCf1.png"></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="4"><li>接下来就可以键入命令下载SCP：SL了<br>输入login anonymous匿名登陆SteamCmd，等待少许时间，当看到OK就代表登陆完成 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Steam&gt;login anonymous</span><br><span class="line">Connecting anonymously to Steam Public...Retrying. . . </span><br><span class="line">OK</span><br><span class="line">Waiting <span class="keyword">for</span> client config...OK</span><br><span class="line">Waiting <span class="keyword">for</span> user info...OK</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>输入 <strong>app_update 996560 validate</strong> 下载SCP：SL，并等待下载安装成功<br>996560就是SCP：SL的序列号 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">app_update <span class="number">996560</span> validate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>待安装成功之后，我们用Xftp找到游戏所在位置<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/12/pSuAzHf.png"></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="5"><li>开服<br>使用cd命令进入方才游戏的路径 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /root/Steam/steamapps/common/SCP\ Secret\ Laboratory\ Dedicated\ Server/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>运行 <strong>LocalAdmin</strong> 文件 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./LocalAdmin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="6"><li>选项<br>EULA协议，我们之前在MineCraft也遇见过，yes通过即可 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">Do</span> you accept the EULA? [yes/no]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>和上面Windows一样，一般来说用你想要的端口号都行，我们回车选择默认7777端口号 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Port number (default: <span class="number">7777</span>): </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>这里我们选择回车，不进行配置，因为默认的配置已经很标准了 <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">Do</span> you want to edit that configuration? [edit/keep]: </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><strong>后面无论提示什么我们一路回车就行了，不做过多赘述了</strong></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><ol start="7"><li>当看到 <strong>Waiting for players…</strong> 时就代表服务器已经开启成功了！ <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="number">2023</span>-<span class="number">01</span>-<span class="number">12</span> <span class="number">11</span>:<span class="number">47</span>:<span class="number">30</span>.<span class="number">652</span> +<span class="number">08</span>:<span class="number">00</span>] Incoming connections will be no longer delayed.</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">2023</span>-<span class="number">01</span>-<span class="number">12</span> <span class="number">11</span>:<span class="number">47</span>:<span class="number">30</span>.<span class="number">655</span> +<span class="number">08</span>:<span class="number">00</span>] Idle <span class="built_in">mode</span> is now available.</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">2023</span>-<span class="number">01</span>-<span class="number">12</span> <span class="number">11</span>:<span class="number">47</span>:<span class="number">30</span>.<span class="number">682</span> +<span class="number">08</span>:<span class="number">00</span>] Waiting <span class="keyword">for</span> players...</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">2023</span>-<span class="number">01</span>-<span class="number">12</span> <span class="number">11</span>:<span class="number">48</span>:<span class="number">00</span>.<span class="number">627</span> +<span class="number">08</span>:<span class="number">00</span>] Server has entered the idle <span class="built_in">mode</span>.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/12/pSuEyrt.png"></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><p>最后！因为Linux关闭shell界面后进程就会结束，所以我们需要安装一个工具（screen）<br> <figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Centos: yum -y install screen</span><br><span class="line">Ubuntu: sudo apt -y install screen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><hr>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
