  <entry>
    <title>MineCraft服务器架设教程[Linux/Windows]</title>
    <link href="http://wooxin.xyz/posts/e10cdec2.html"/>
    <id>http://wooxin.xyz/posts/e10cdec2.html</id>
    <published>2023-01-09T04:27:17.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-01-11T13:24:18.153Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h2 id="一：准备工作-amp-前言"><a href="#一：准备工作-amp-前言" class="headerlink" title="一：准备工作 &amp; 前言"></a>一：准备工作 &amp; 前言</h2><blockquote><p>一台电脑（Linux&#x2F;Windown）</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>一个MineCraftServer核心</p><blockquote><p>如：<a href="https://papermc.io/downloads">Paper</a></p></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>对应核心版本的Java</p><blockquote><p>如：<a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/">JDK19</a></p></blockquote></blockquote><hr><h2 id="二：硬件选择"><a href="#二：硬件选择" class="headerlink" title="二：硬件选择"></a>二：硬件选择</h2><blockquote><ol><li>MineCraft是一个吃CPU主频的游戏，如果你想让你服务器的玩家流畅的游玩必须要保证CPU主频够高</li><li>MineCraft比较吃单核性能，也就是说你的CPU核心够多的话是可以在一台电脑上开多个服务器的</li><li>MineCraft这个游戏对内存的要求没那么高，1333MHz就足够了，内存的大小决定了服务器最大人数，所以如果要开一个50人的服务器最少要有16G内存</li><li>服务器带宽也是最重要的一个因素了，带宽越高服务器能承载的玩家数量也越多，玩家游玩的体验也就越高</li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><p>举个CPU例子</p><blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="center">CPU</th><th align="center">内存</th><th align="center">带宽</th><th align="center">玩家数</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">2.5GHz</td><td align="center">8G</td><td align="center">5Mbps</td><td align="center">10</td></tr><tr><td align="center">2.5GHz</td><td align="center">8G</td><td align="center">50Mbps</td><td align="center">20</td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>可以看到，当相同的在相同配置下只增加带宽服务器成才能力提升比较<strong>微弱</strong><br>这是因为<strong>CPU的性能瓶颈</strong>导致服务器承载玩家的能力不够强大</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>再举个CPU例子</p><blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="center">CPU</th><th align="center">内存</th><th align="center">带宽</th><th align="center">玩家数</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">5.0GHz</td><td align="center">16G</td><td align="center">5Mbps</td><td align="center">10</td></tr><tr><td align="center">5.0GHz</td><td align="center">16G</td><td align="center">50Mbps</td><td align="center">70</td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>可以看到，再增强了CPU性能之后服务器可以承载的玩家数量直接提升了一大截<br>本人开过很长时间的MineCraft服务器，所以在下方推荐几个配置<br><strong>注：本人开的是插件服务器</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>推荐</p><blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="center">玩家数量</th><th align="center">CPU频率</th><th align="center">内存</th><th align="center">带宽</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">50</td><td align="center">&gt; 4.0GHz</td><td align="center">&gt; 16G</td><td align="center">&gt; 30Mbps</td></tr><tr><td align="center">100</td><td align="center">&gt; 5.0GHz</td><td align="center">&gt; 40G</td><td align="center">&gt; 50Mbps</td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>博主的服务器</p><blockquote><table><thead><tr><th align="center">玩家数量</th><th align="center">CPU频率</th><th align="center">内存</th><th align="center">带宽</th><th align="center">服务器数量</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">130左右</td><td align="center">5.2GHz</td><td align="center">128G</td><td align="center">1400Mbps</td><td align="center">12</td></tr></tbody></table></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>如果你的CPU主频够高，且核心数量较多，可以选择多开服务器，比如你的CPU有12个核心，那你就能开9个服务器，剩下的要留给冗余<br>比如开一个主城服[Bungee]多个子服</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="三：服务器部署-Windows"><a href="#三：服务器部署-Windows" class="headerlink" title="三：服务器部署[Windows]"></a>三：服务器部署[Windows]</h2><blockquote><p>先准备好我们的<a href="https://papermc.io/downloads"><strong>服务器核心</strong></a>和<a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/"><strong>JDK19</strong></a>，并且在电脑内安装JDK</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>新建一个CMD文件，并填写：<strong>java -jar 核心,jar -nogui</strong><br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/10/pSm8uQO.png"></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>运行CMD文件后等待约10秒左右，CMD文件会自己关闭，并出现这些文件<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/10/pSm8a6S.png"></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>我们打开【eula.txt】文件，并将eula&#x3D;false改为eula&#x3D;true<br> <figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#By changing the setting below to TRUE you are indicating your agreement to our EULA (https://aka.ms/MinecraftEULA).</span><br><span class="line">#Tue Jan 10 20:10:05 CST 2023</span><br><span class="line">eula=true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>继续运行CMD文件，当你的CMD命令窗口出现这些字的时候就代表服务器已经启动成功了<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="number">20</span>:<span class="number">26</span>:<span class="number">03</span> INFO]: Done (<span class="number">4</span>.<span class="number">259</span>s)! <span class="keyword">For</span> <span class="built_in">help</span>, <span class="built_in">type</span> &quot;<span class="built_in">help</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">20</span>:<span class="number">26</span>:<span class="number">03</span> INFO]: Timings Reset</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>如图：<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/10/pSmGhgf.png"></p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="四：服务器部署-Linux"><a href="#四：服务器部署-Linux" class="headerlink" title="四：服务器部署[Linux]"></a>四：服务器部署[Linux]</h2><blockquote><p>先准备好我们的<a href="https://papermc.io/downloads"><strong>服务器核心</strong></a>和<a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/"><strong>JDK19</strong></a><br>这里要注意，因为我们是Linux系统，所以不能直接下载.exe的JDK<br>我们需要下载.tar.gz为结尾的JDK文件以自定义安装位置，方便在Linux上进行维护<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/10/pSmJLee.png"></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>将准备好的<strong>JDK</strong>和<strong>服务器核心</strong>放入root目录（这里使用的工具是<a href="https://www.xshell.com/zh/free-for-home-school/"><strong>Xftp</strong></a>和<a href="https://www.xshell.com/zh/free-for-home-school/"><strong>Xshell</strong></a>）<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/10/pSmYpSP.png"></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>打开Xshell，输入ls，查看文件是否无误<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@Cnetos2 ~]# ls</span><br><span class="line">jdk-<span class="number">19</span>_linux-x64_bin.tar.gz  paper-<span class="number">1</span>.<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">3</span>-<span class="number">372</span>.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>查验无误后，我们就可以在Linux内安装JDK了<br>首先，我们输入以下命令，解压<strong>jdk-19_linux-x64_bin.tar.gz</strong><br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zvxf jdk-<span class="number">19</span>_linux-x64_bin.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>解压完成后，Root目录会出现一个jdk-19.0.1文件<br>一般来说我推荐将前置类的软件都安装到&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local目录，这会很方便维护<br>将jdk-19.0.1文件移动到&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local目录<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mv jdk-<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span>/ /usr/local</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>打开&#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile文件</p><blockquote><p>这里推荐用Xftp找到&#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile文件，用记事本打开进行编辑<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/10/pSmNDJA.png"></p></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>在profile文件的最底部添加如下内容<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># JDK</span><br><span class="line">export JAVA_HOME=/usr/local/jdk-<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span> #这是JDK的安装路径，如果你把JDK装到其他地方就要更改此路径</span><br><span class="line">export JRE_HOME=$&#123;JAVA_HOME&#125;/jre</span><br><span class="line">export CLASSPATH=.:$&#123;JAVA_HOME&#125;/lib:$&#123;JRE_HOME&#125;/lib:$CLASSPATH</span><br><span class="line">export JAVA_PATH=$&#123;JAVA_HOME&#125;/bin:$&#123;JRE_HOME&#125;/bin</span><br><span class="line">export <span class="built_in">PATH</span>=$<span class="built_in">PATH</span>:$&#123;JAVA_PATH&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>然后输入source &#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile重载profile<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>最后，我们输入java -version查看是否安装成功<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@Cnetos2 ~]# java -version</span><br><span class="line">java version &quot;<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span>&quot; <span class="number">2022</span>-<span class="number">10</span>-<span class="number">18</span></span><br><span class="line">Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build <span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span>+<span class="number">10</span>-<span class="number">21</span>)</span><br><span class="line">Java HotSpot(TM) <span class="number">64</span>-Bit Server VM (build <span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span>+<span class="number">10</span>-<span class="number">21</span>, mixed <span class="built_in">mode</span>, sharing)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>出现如上内容就说明JDK安装成功了<br>我们已经可以进行开服了</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>首先使用mkdir命令创建一个名为MineCraftServer的文件夹<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@Cnetos2 ~]# <span class="built_in">mkdir</span> MineCraftServer</span><br><span class="line">[root@Cnetos2 ~]# ls</span><br><span class="line">MineCraftServer  paper-<span class="number">1</span>.<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">3</span>-<span class="number">372</span>.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>将paper-1.19.3-372.jar服务器核心移动到MineCraftServer文件夹<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mv paper-<span class="number">1</span>.<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">3</span>-<span class="number">372</span>.jar MineCraftServer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>接着使用cd命令进入MineCraftServer文件<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> MineCraftServer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>创建XXX.sh文件<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi <span class="number">1</span>.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>在1.sh文件中添加如下内容（与上方Windows里的一样）<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -jar paper-<span class="number">1</span>.<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">3</span>-<span class="number">372</span>.jar -nogui</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>为1.sh文件提升权限使其可以运行<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod <span class="number">777</span> <span class="number">1</span>.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>运行1.sh开启服务器<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./<span class="number">1</span>.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>然后显示如下内容<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Starting org.bukkit.craftbukkit.Main</span><br><span class="line">System Info: Java <span class="number">19</span> (Java HotSpot(TM) <span class="number">64</span>-Bit Server VM <span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">0</span>.<span class="number">1</span>+<span class="number">10</span>-<span class="number">21</span>) Host: Linux <span class="number">3</span>.<span class="number">10</span>.<span class="number">0</span>-<span class="number">1160</span>.el7.x86_64 (amd64)</span><br><span class="line">Loading libraries, please wait...</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">21</span>:<span class="number">37</span>:<span class="number">40</span> INFO]: Building unoptimized datafixer</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">21</span>:<span class="number">37</span>:<span class="number">43</span> ERROR]: Failed to load properties from file: server.properties</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">21</span>:<span class="number">37</span>:<span class="number">43</span> WARN]: Failed to load eula.txt</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">21</span>:<span class="number">37</span>:<span class="number">43</span> INFO]: You need to agree to the EULA <span class="keyword">in</span> order to run the server. Go to eula.txt <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="built_in">more</span> info.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>我们需要打开EULA协议<br>我们打开【eula.txt】文件，并将eula&#x3D;false改为eula&#x3D;true<br> <figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#By changing the setting below to TRUE you are indicating your agreement to our EULA (https://aka.ms/MinecraftEULA).</span><br><span class="line">#Tue Jan 10 20:10:05 CST 2023</span><br><span class="line">eula=true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>然后继续运行1.sh，当出现如下内容时即代表开服成功<br> <figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="number">20</span>:<span class="number">26</span>:<span class="number">03</span> INFO]: Done (<span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">856</span>s)! <span class="keyword">For</span> <span class="built_in">help</span>, <span class="built_in">type</span> &quot;<span class="built_in">help</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">20</span>:<span class="number">26</span>:<span class="number">03</span> INFO]: Timings Reset</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>如图：<br><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/10/pSmB3Je.png"></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>最后！因为Linux关闭shell界面后进程就会结束，所以我们需要安装一个工具（screen）<br> <figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Centos: yum -y install screen</span><br><span class="line">Ubuntu: sudo apt -y install screen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></blockquote><hr>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
